arStrings.szText: Kills have a {c_number}[Affix_Value_1]%{/c} chance to summon a {c_important}Wolf Companion{/c} to your side for {c_random}[Affix_Value_2]{/c} seconds. This effect is a {c_label}Lucky Hit{/c} against bosses. In addition, gain {c_number}+[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} Ranks to {c_important}Wolves{/c}.
